## No Backend (Local Storage Only)

Your app is configured to work entirely with local storage using SharedPreferences. No backend setup required!

### Features Available
- ✅ Local user data persistence
- ✅ Session management
- ✅ Profile management (stored locally)
- ❌ Data synchronization across devices
- ❌ Real-time updates
- ❌ Server-side validation

### When to Add a Backend
Consider adding a backend when you need:
- Multi-device synchronization
- Real-time features
- Server-side business logic
- Enhanced security
- User data backup
